longBusinessSummary: XP Chemistries AB (publ), a biotechnology company, develops and produces forest-based capsaicin and analogues. It offers animal feed ingredients, personal care and cosmetic ingredients, pure capsaicinoids, and self-defense spray ingredients. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Sundsvall, Sweden.
